E L I 🤍 I absolutely love being your mommy and watching you grow and seeing your personality begin to emerge from your tiny baby body 🤍 You are such a blessing to our family and I can’t believe I lived life without you in it. My heart NEEDED you, sweet baby boy!! If possible, stop growing so fast! 𝗜 𝗹𝗼𝘃𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗳𝗼𝗿𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗿, 𝗜’𝗹𝗹 𝗹𝗶𝗸𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗮𝗹𝘄𝗮𝘆𝘀, 𝗮𝘀 𝗹𝗼𝗻𝗴 𝗮𝘀 𝗜’𝗺 𝗹𝗶𝘃𝗶𝗻𝗴, 𝗺𝘁 𝗯𝗮𝗯𝘆 𝘆𝗼𝘂’𝗹𝗹 𝗯𝗲. .
